  "title": "🏭 Production Line (Factory) Assistants X 30, Aircon ❄️Choose Morning | Afternoon | Night Shifts ⏰",
  "description": "<p>🚀 <strong>FAST SHORTLISTING | IMMEDIATE START</strong></p><p>We are hiring <strong>temporary Production Operators</strong> to perform <strong>simple assembly work</strong> involving plastic tubings for a <strong>minimum period of 1–3 months or MORE</strong></p><p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Ang Mo Kio Industrial Park (AMK)<br />📄 <strong>Employment Type:</strong> Min. 1 month (contract)<br />💵 <strong>Salary:</strong> $11–$12 per hour (Earn up to <strong>$2.2K+</strong>)<br />📅 <strong>Working Days:</strong> Monday to Saturday (6-day work week)<br />🧼 <strong>Work Environment:</strong> Air-conditioned, clean room</p><p>⏰ <strong>Working Hours (Choose ONE):</strong><br />• AM Shift: 7am – 3pm<br />• PM Shift: 3pm – 11pm<br />• MN Shift: 11pm – 7am</p><p>🔧 <strong>Job Scope:</strong><br />• Simple assembling duties<br />• Wire insertion & lightweight product handling<br />• Good eyesight required (no colour blindness)<br />• Required to wear smock & hairnet (clean room)</p><p>📲 <strong>Apply Now!</strong><br />WhatsApp your <strong>RESUME</strong> to <strong>8891 4996</strong><br />🆔 <strong>Job Code:</strong> POAMK</p><p>—<br /><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</em></p><p>CREW by HRNet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd (24C2435)<br />👤 <strong>Athirah Bte Rosli (R2197227)</strong></p>",
